ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵條撚做咩</blockquote><br />\n另一個原因 睇你搭邊間airline, 國泰就會快d 因爲佢停機位近行李運輸帶, 如果你落機要搭多程鐵路先到入境大堂（如香X), 因為距離太遠, 以我經驗你預行李至少落機後半小時才到<br />\n<br />\n一分錢 一分貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔一定，有時你太近嘅閘口會快過啲行李，反而遠少少你可能出到嚟已經有"},{"pid":"18359a1cffbf75ddd3e120892f8611faa8c6f2f7","tid":103591,"uid":53509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我次次去日本都係行李等我<br />\n番香港就我等行李<br />\n快則半個鐘, 慢既1個鐘都走唔到</blockquote><br />\n你係日本入境唔駛排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算要排都好快，日本基本上可以land咗一個鐘後，已經可以拎哂行李等緊巴士或者電車，上埋車都試過<br />\n香港就慢慢等，去個廁所，吹個水，食包薯片都未出你架機d行李呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b8fcd90c27c822e08880f596316b89fbef1174","tid":103591,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"講起都覺，有次等咗九個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同支那接軌啦，排名應該跌出頭十先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3272afccd042b1df006d8bf76abdd2e19dbad879","tid":103591,"uid":1612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:54:55.000Z","msg":"真係好Q慢....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0422603304dbb5dbf4a7d71697b1b02725351f3","tid":103591,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"香港有邊行係人手夠 <br />\n個個老細出手低 <br />\n佢地無諗過員工係你生財工具 <br />\n工欲善其事 必先利其器"},{"pid":"d0b1f9564f28e763e176c8d299a2502859f7a5de","tid":103591,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"試過等一粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14117a1016fb1c778a08652a147d041cad65c9e6","tid":103591,"uid":26793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"咁撚低人工 又辛苦 撚有人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a544d05c82ec522c5936904153e277fc7dd9fc7","tid":103591,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>機場成堆垃圾工<br />\n搭車來回3粒鐘<br />\n食飯搭車冇3000蚊<br />\n但15000up已經算好撚高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係市區搵份9工都有呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵條撚做咩</blockquote><br />\n另一個原因 睇你搭邊間airline, 國泰就會快d 因爲佢停機位近行李運輸帶, 如果你落機要搭多程鐵路先到入境大堂（如香X), 因為距離太遠, 以我經驗你預行李至少落機後半小時才到<br />\n<br />\n一分錢 一分貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔一定，有時你太近嘅閘口會快過啲行李，反而遠少少你可能出到嚟已經有</blockquote><br />\n最正都係落2x~3x閘 唔遠唔近岩岩好 落機又有屎坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb568a67eed6cea5b9059a6e6acf005ad98ff5f","tid":103591,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"之前有個post已經講過，<br />\n根本除左機師係人工奇高之外，<br />\n其他航空業嘅工，出手都係奇低（包括空姐、包ATC）。<br />\n<br />\n你見永遠公營機構高層其實都係同一班人，<br />\n只係一個機構任期夠就轉去第二個機構咁。<br />\n官僚，冇新思維。<br />\n<br />\n依家機場起豬西大橋整到溶溶爛爛，<br />\n應該放錢擴建嘅唔放，係要嘥錢喺啲濕鳩嘢。<br />\n<br />\n以前會為個機場而自豪，但依家唔會。<br />\n尤其搭親飛機返嚟都見到等行李寫住延誤。"},{"pid":"2032636f85f5d046612ae8abaf5eea7ef4f942c1","tid":103591,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:10:02.000Z","msg":"十次有九次返香港都係行李等我<br />\n<br />\n利申：因航金卡"},{"pid":"4f7346c7d35c74040cbba6a1949e576a3ff0e7e2","tid":103591,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我次次去日本都係行李等我<br />\n番香港就我等行李<br />\n快則半個鐘, 慢既1個鐘都走唔到</blockquote><br />\n你係日本入境唔駛排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算要排都好快，日本基本上可以land咗一個鐘後，已經可以拎哂行李等緊巴士或者電車，上埋車都試過<br />\n香港就慢慢等，去個廁所，吹個水，食包薯片都未出你架機d行李呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港慢係事實，所以有寄倉返香港鳩衝落機係ON9.我飛TPE KIX SIN, 正路開機門計廿分鐘左右點都出到行李<br />\n<br />\n唔駛排隊? 有張卡咪唔駛排(咁長囉)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fa2c1455bee3266820c940889a6b181d287f94","tid":103591,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機場成堆垃圾工<br />\n搭車來回3粒鐘<br />\n食飯搭車冇3000蚊<br />\n但15000up已經算好撚高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係市區搵份9工都有呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵條撚做咩</blockquote><br />\n另一個原因 睇你搭邊間airline, 國泰就會快d 因爲佢停機位近行李運輸帶, 如果你落機要搭多程鐵路先到入境大堂（如香X), 因為距離太遠, 以我經驗你預行李至少落機後半小時才到<br />\n<br />\n一分錢 一分貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因航睇機隊調動<br />\n如果你班機跟手飛歐洲，你預佢停6x gate都得"},{"pid":"62e186c6baa1efa7af63d9a003a5989fb564197f","tid":103591,"uid":16647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"因為香港入境實在太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6499a9311df97b0b5e61be5d2a018282bfcbd4b5","tid":103591,"uid":73247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機場成堆垃圾工<br />\n搭車來回3粒鐘<br />\n食飯搭車冇3000蚊<br />\n但15000up已經算好撚高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係市區搵份9工都有呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵條撚做咩</blockquote><br />\n另一個原因 睇你搭邊間airline, 國泰就會快d 因爲佢停機位近行李運輸帶, 如果你落機要搭多程鐵路先到入境大堂（如香X), 因為距離太遠, 以我經驗你預行李至少落機後半小時才到<br />\n<br />\n一分錢 一分貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我兩個月前搭國泰都同我delay左成粒鐘咁濟"},{"pid":"d88393ee555fb0016e8fbbac45318bb0b644b794","tid":103591,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為香港入境實在太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nE道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但快左D時間用黎等行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb28e855f7e681dc44e0447b5b7616b273885b4","tid":103591,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:34:01.000Z","msg":"試過幾次等45分鐘<br />\n其他機場未試過咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5500bb717ebed2810092e1e8117cf83b7e7e200","tid":103591,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港依個西社會<br />\n<br />\n只係會將功勞將利益 畀哂 最上層個班所謂管理層<br />\n<br />\n邊一行都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n但往往最值得加許既 就係最下層個班人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a136012dd36d2950749dca61ba49248e660a638","tid":103591,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"宏觀上真係要擴建東涌新市鎮，增勞動人口；另外，機場待遇真係閪，交通飲食補貼唔夠，最直接係加人工。"},{"pid":"c6f6aa0b9b853af4cb836271bf66c49d46b8159d","tid":103591,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"東涌d人特登搭幾個字地鐵出市區返工，機場就反而唔夠人手<br />\n好一個資源錯配"},{"pid":"cb6539f4c0172a49df588df61cd266bdb612027d","tid":103591,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"強制綜援狗做咪得"},{"pid":"c17bc1aeb11bfa5feb10bddb81c4437ea57c315b","tid":103591,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"可以Backpack就backpack上機<br />\n地勤會偷嘢"},{"pid":"b4d3b8829559b614a64e29fd716d6fd888489e33","tid":103591,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep