chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計返時間就知香港耐啦<br />\n去日本係要排，但係排半個鐘到一出去就見到行李到晒<br />\n香港過完關都重要等起碼45分鐘啲行李先開始出"},{"pid":"d9f3f3f8697d6d397b32a1c3eb04e0e19bf95156","tid":103591,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"日本使鬼排咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩三年去咗十幾次日本<br />\n我淨係去沖繩果次要排隊排成半粒鐘<br />\n其他一係就無人唔使排 (包括: kix hnd ngo fuk cts)<br />\n一係就5分鐘內已經過埋關<br />\n啲行李已經喺運輸帶轉緊圈"},{"pid":"6032cad2ab1c34d159369871e06e30448780824d","tid":103591,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"慢就慢啦 賴e道快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125c54d52ff13903086870317e71b51955a7dc63","tid":103591,"uid":37729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實d 行李係唔係一定跟你坐既機去？<br />\n聽人講過會用第二部機送</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會 9成9同一架機 確保航機安全"},{"pid":"5739207d89a13cd4729317083c47c4e2595c2d42","tid":103591,"uid":37729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"講開可以講埋 新個個中場簡直無用腦諗野<br />\n竟然無行李帶運輸 要用車車番過大樓先做<br />\n點做得快呀"},{"pid":"001b435401c073d86518b6cfcf00e78a71ae6701","tid":103591,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講開可以講埋 新個個中場簡直無用腦諗野<br />\n竟然無行李帶運輸 要用車車番過大樓先做<br />\n點做得快呀</blockquote><br />\n同北衛星, T2 一樣咁戇鳩"},{"pid":"ac0b32289a2a4207cd2b3146322c1e979467533f","tid":103591,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講開可以講埋 新個個中場簡直無用腦諗野<br />\n竟然無行李帶運輸 要用車車番